import React from 'react'
import Accordion from 'react-bootstrap/Accordion';
import { Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"
import "../Assests/css files/Accordian.css"
const Accordian = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Row>
       
     
      <Accordion>
      <Col md={6}>

</Col>
       

      </Accordion>
      </Row>
    </>
  )
}

export default Accordian
